===Proper noun===
'''Leo'''

#A male given name, sometimes a short form of [[Leonard]]; compare [[Leon]].
#One of the [[constellation]]s of the [[zodiac]], shaped approximately like a [[lion]].
#The zodiac sign for the [[Lion]], covering July 23 - August 22.

